/*
Rotary Encoder and Buzzer Program for Raspberry Pi 4 Model B

This program reads rotation data from a rotary encoder connected to GPIO pins 23 (CLK) and 24 (DT),
generates different frequency tones on a passive buzzer connected to GPIO pin 20, and implements interrupt-driven
encoder reading with robust error handling for GPIO setup and PWM generation.

Compilation:
